      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the<strong> chopped creamed coconut </strong>in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
