    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped shallot</strong>, <strong>ginger</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>lime leaves</strong> and <strong>ground turmeric </strong>to a<strong> food processor</strong> with the<strong> chopped red chilli</strong> and<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Blitz into a paste – this is your<strong> fiery sambal</strong></p><p>Tip: No food processor? Chop everything up as finely as you can and mix it together!</p>",
