    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the fiery sambal<strong> </strong>is cooking, dissolve the <strong>tamarind paste</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar </strong>and the <strong>soy sauce</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>tamarind stock</strong></p>",
